                <td align="center" style="min-width: 590px;">
                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="590" style="min-width: 590px; background-color: white; padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px; border-collapse:separate; border: none;">
                        <tr><td valign="top" style="font-size: 13px;">
                            <div>
                                  <p></p>
                                <p>Hello <b><t t-out="object.user_id.partner_id.name" /></b>,</p>
                                <p>Your person profile has been successfully created on the HWSETA Hub ERP system.</p>
                                  <p>If you are a stakeholder of HWSETA requiring access to stakeholder activities please proceed with either SDF or Org Rep registration depending on your current status.</p>
                                  <p><br></br></p>
                                <p>Regards</p>
                                <p>HWSETA Hub ERP system</p>
                              </div>
